This theme is based on a _Jekyll_ theme with the same name.

### Setting

Custom settings available in the `state` folder starting from the location of this file.

- To hide the site header, set the `header` state value to `false`.
- To hide the site navigation, set the `nav` state value to `false`.
- To hide the site links, set the `links` state value to `false`.
- Limit the maximum links displayed in site navigation by setting the `nav` state value as numbers to describe the limit.
- Set your custom links URL in the `links` state. There are `envelope` and `github` item available.
- To enable dark mode, set the `dark` state to `true`.

### Embedded Content

You can also embed a lot of stuff, for example from _YouTube_. To scale the video to full width use the `<div class="embed"></div>` wrapper around the iframe. Use `<div class="large"></div>` wrapper to increase the width of an image or iframe.

